parameters: Shopkeeper: "!!"

Pony-Celeste: "You're the owner of Yaoyahachi... aren't you?"
Pony-Celeste: "Are you hurt?"
Shopkeeper: "Ah, yes... But who might you be?"
Shopkeeper: "Pony-Celeste!!"
Shopkeeper: "You came to save me."
Shopkeeper: "I was caught by Zaida-Gu, I thought I was done for."
Shopkeeper: "My life has been saved. How can I ever repay you..."

Pony-Celeste: "Protecting the lives of the townspeople is my mission
after all!"
Pony-Celeste: "Now, let's get out of here."

Pony-Celeste: "Everyone is waiting for Yaoyahachi-san's fresh
vegetables!"
01_ポニーセレス_デフォルトA
Shopkeeper: "...Ah, that's right. You're absolutely correct."
Shopkeeper: "I can't afford to be downcast."

Shopkeeper: "I have to start from scratch, find a new contract farmer,
and work hard to deliver fresh vegetables again."

Pony-Celeste: "Ahaha, that's the spirit. I'm also looking forward to
seeing Yaoyahachi-san's vegetables on the dining table!"
